lead_paragraph: A letter from St. Petersburg announces the death of Dr. Frachn, aged 69, Conservator of the imperial Asiatic Museum of that city. He was the author of several works on Oriental numismatics, and has left behind a fine collection of Eastern coins, 20,000 in number, some of which are unique.

headline.main: FOREIGN INTELLIGENCE; FROM OUR EUROPEAN FILES. Miscellaneous.
